description:
Today Bihar Evening news on 07th march Sudham,  Kabaddi World Cup 2025, National Lok Adalat, Pipa bridge.  
#newsbihar #eveningbiharnews #biharnewslivetoday #todaybiharnews #aajkabiharnews #Biharnewshindi #biharkanews  #todaynewsbihar #biharboardnewupdate # # #

1. Railways' special plan for passenger convenience at major stations of Bihar

2. Education Minister answered the question of teachers' salary

3. CM Nitish launched the first export consignment of Sudha

4. Kabaddi World Cup 2025 will be organized in Rajgir

5. National Drama Festival will be organized in Begusarai, Bihar

6. Special trains will run from 8 to 13 March in view of Holi

7. National Lok Adalat will be organized on 8 March

8. Pipa bridge connecting Bihar and UP is ready

9. Four-lane road will be constructed in this district of Bihar

10. Action on liquor smuggling case before Holi

11. CM Nitish appealed to the opposition parties to remain calm with folded hands

12. BJP's counterattack on Tejashwi's promise of domicile policy

13. Hearing will be held in the court on March 22 regarding Tejashwi and Mukesh Sahni in this case

14. Budget session Vijay Sinha, who reached Delhi midway, met Gadkari

15. Umpires announced before the match between India and New Zealand
